{"tid":991082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【三隧分流】消息：政府擬撤回方案　陳帆下午4時見傳媒料交代","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T10:55:07.000Z","uid":26418,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6974c2e12a31fe57517274854becc6a682a22b","tid":991082,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"政府明日（23日）將在立法會就「三隧分流」收費調整方案提無約束力議案。有消息指，政府擬撤回有關方案。運輸及房屋局今日下午2時發出新聞稿，指運房局局長陳帆、運輸署署長陳美寶和路政署署長陳派明今日下午4時在政府總部會見傳媒，料會談及三隧分流方案最新進展事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/286007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F286007&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=10c35d81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/286007</a>"},{"pid":"7f611f5a0cb4f697fe1369ad56e4b0ca045e600e","tid":991082,"uid":26418,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"中環灣仔繞道已經搞到西隧咁塞 仲講分流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e9c8be8df61288e6142b90a08375b3a15600af","tid":991082,"uid":141151,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到係威係勢，上埋北京遊說<br />\n竟然繞道通車兩日後就縮沙？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下保皇派點做"},{"pid":"0bcc0faf981857e44c3a42035a6f6b45b6fd5da0","tid":991082,"uid":2126,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"話商業機密唔可以事先透露<br />\n傾完就話冇得改, 冇得唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲惡過共產黨<br />